00:04:21,648 --> 00:04:24,570
bouncing around ideas what the project would be.

50
00:04:24,570 --> 00:04:28,852
And on February 2019, we started full production.

51
00:04:29,771 --> 00:04:35,074
Generally, I was aiming for pretty tight production timelines of smaller projects in which we

52
00:04:35,074 --> 00:04:40,477
could spend about a year to a year and a half producing something that would then in turn

53
00:04:40,477 --> 00:04:48,101
give us more runway in terms of diversifying our game portfolio and future-proofing the

